track_notes:
About 30 minutes. See the description.

Mid/High hiking boots recommended.
The climb is very easy, mainly on a forest road that will take us almost to the top. Once we reach the last stretch of the road, we will have to walk a little off the path on easy tracks.

Pot na Veliki Rogatec poteka po gozdnih vlakah. Avto sva parkirala nekoliko naprej od prve gozdne vlake, na katero stopimo iz gozdne ceste. Sedaj, maja meseca, je teren že precej poraščen s podrastjem, zato računajte s klopi. Zadnji del poti poteka po brezpotju, strmo navzgor v hrib. Na vrhu je izredno malo prostora. Razgledov ni nobenih. Vrh je poraščen. Čas, porabljen za vzpon je okoli 45 minut. Ste povsem v območju medveda zato poskušajte biti nekoliko bolj hrupni, da se žival lahko umakne.

We parked the car a bit away from the first forest track where you leave the forest road.
Now, in May, the terrain is already quite overgrown with underbrush, so be prepared for ticks.
The final part of the trail goes off-trail, steeply uphill.
There is very little space at the top.
There are no views—the summit is overgrown.
The ascent takes about 45 minutes. Brown bear lives here so try to make some noise.

73, Aleksander, S57S  May 2025
